ton.com/properties/1-harrington-gardens/" target="_blank">1 Harrington Gardens</a>, which are to a lesser specification and budget.  Rates for both serviced residences are <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="London serviced residences three months stay" href="http://www.theharrington.com/availability/" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Location:</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">3 and 1 Harrington Gardens are perfectly located for a longer stay – just 2 minutes’ walk from Gloucester Road tube station, with direct routes to the rest of central London.  There are many shops, supermarkets and restaurants in the immediate vicinity.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Many of London’s main museums are close by. Kensington Gardens and Hyde Park are 10 minutes’ walk and major shopping areas are a short tube ride away.  The Harrington is also close to London’s Earl’s Court and Olympia.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Don’t forget to book your apartment securely at <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="London serviced residences three months stay" href="http://www.theharrington.com/properties/3-harrington-gardens/3-harrington-gardens/" target="_blank">The Harrington web site</a>, on our special rates for London serviced residences three months stay.</p>', 'London Serviced Residences Three Months Stay', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'london-serviced-residences-three-months-stay', '', '', '2014-06-20 15:25:21', '2014-06-20 15:25:21', '', 217, 'http://localhost/v2.theharrington.com/?page_id=225', 0, 'page', '', 0),
